data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3 bed 2 bath newer construction ranch home! GREAT curb appeal -Beautifully landscaped w/ brick flower beds & sod for true green grass. Covered front porch for overhead shelter & a ring doorbell for added security. New front door w/glass pane windows. Step inside to the open living area with plenty of natural lighting, plus recessed LED lights. 1/2'' real wood stained treated oakwood throughout the living room, kitchen, dining room, & hallway. Open to dining area, the kitchen features soft close cream cabinets w/ brushed chrome handles, lots of granite counters, an island, new dishwasher, & stainless steel appliances. Large bedrooms, primary bedroom w/an ensuite large WCI & full bath w/soft close cabinets & a double sink. 1st floor laundry w/new cabinets. Fenced backyard w/covered patio, 2.5 car garage w/large custom work bench & plenty of space for storage. New air conditioner & tankless water heater plus more! Flag pole in front excluded. Most furniture & TV is for sale negotiable in separate bill of sale. Don't miss the chance to make this home yours!
